Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.26,0:02:48.27,6-normal,,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,900)\fs80\bord3\blur0\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H000000&\pos(1827,886)\b1}#6  Sang{\c&H138BC6&} Raja, {\c&H000000&}Ber{\c&H138BC6&}sungguh{\c&H000000&}-sungguh.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:03.05,0:00:05.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, ini dungeon paling bawah?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:07.25,0:00:08.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cantik sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:08.85,0:00:10.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada banyak kristal.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:11.01,0:00:13.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Rasanya hangat dan nyaman.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:13.98,0:00:16.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ditambah, aku baru pertama kali\Nmelihat bunga seperti ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:17.61,0:00:19.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Perasaanku tidak enak.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:19.85,0:00:22.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa ada kabut di suhu sehangat ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:26.21,0:00:28.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada apa, Note?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:28.61,0:00:29.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bunga ini...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:30.41,0:00:32.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya kita baru saja melewatinya.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:33.21,0:00:34.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Masa, sih?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:34.35,0:00:37.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita masuk dari sebelah sana, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:37.58,0:00:40.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, kenapa ada pintu masuk\Ndi sebelah sana?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:42.21,0:00:44.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak, bukankah pintu masuknya cuma satu?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:44.68,0:00:45.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:45.71,0:00:47.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak melihat ada pintu masuk.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:47.38,0:00:48.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau lihat ke mana, sih?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:48.91,0:00:50.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jelas-jelas ada di sebelah sana.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:51.91,0:00:54.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak, aku juga tak melihatnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:54.51,0:00:55.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa yang terjadi?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:56.41,0:01:01.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apakah kabut ini menciptakan ilusi\Nyang berbeda bagi tiap orang?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:01.98,0:01:05.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya kabut ini\Nmemanipulasi pikiran kita.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:05.71,0:01:09.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Semuanya, jangan teralihkan\Noleh apa yang kalian lihat!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:43.45,0:02:46.65,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Pancaindraku terasa lumpuh.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:48.55,0:02:49.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Elijah!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:51.55,0:02:53.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo keluar dari sini sekarang.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:53.55,0:02:54.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hah?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:54.55,0:02:56.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan jadi pengecut.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:56.55,0:02:59.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Takkan terlambat untuk keluar\Nsetelah menemukan batu sihir.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:59.41,0:03:01.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana kalau kita\Ntak bisa keluar dari sini?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:02.18,0:03:05.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akan mudah jika kau terus mengikutiku.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:05.21,0:03:07.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Padahal Brald sedang terluka parah.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:07.98,0:03:10.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku setuju, lebih baik kita lanjut.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:10.55,0:03:11.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:11.31,0:03:12.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:12.41,0:03:15.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita akan dapat gelar\Njika berhasil menaklukkan dungeon ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.18,0:03:20.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tanggung rasanya kalau menyerah\Nsaat sudah sejauh ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.38,0:03:22.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak mau pulang dengan tangan kosong.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:22.41,0:03:24.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pulang saja kalau kau mau.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:24.45,0:03:27.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kurasa lebih baik Brald yang jadi ketua.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:27.78,0:03:31.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Note, kurasa kita harus\Nmenyelesaikan misi ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:31.65,0:03:32.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ikutlah bersamaku.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:33.11,0:03:34.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu dulu!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:34.58,0:03:36.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada apa dengan kalian?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.45,0:03:40.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya hasrat mereka dikendalikan\Nsejak masuk ke sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.71,0:03:42.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Note, apa yang harus kita lakukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:43.61,0:03:45.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita harus menyeret mereka keluar.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.85,0:03:49.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Clara?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.45,0:03:52.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini benar-benar kau?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.05,0:03:55.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Criol.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.01,0:03:57.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah kuduga...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.71,0:04:00.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tak mungkin kau sudah mati.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.61,0:04:03.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan pergi!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.21,0:04:04.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:04.45,0:04:06.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akan kujemput kau!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:08.21,0:04:10.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu, Criol!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.65,0:04:12.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Criol!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:13.55,0:04:18.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kabut ini mengubah hasrat kita\Nmenjadi ilusi, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:22.78,0:04:23.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kakak.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.45,0:04:25.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lucas.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:26.21,0:04:27.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.51,0:04:29.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Keluarga Wykes adalah
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.15,0:04:33.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,keluarga terpandang yang membawa Sapin\Nmenang dalam Perang Elenoir.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.01,0:04:36.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita adalah bangsawan sedari lahir.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.18,0:04:41.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Meraih kemenangan, apa pun yang terjadi,\Nadalah bukti keluarga kita.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.11,0:04:47.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kelak, kau pasti bisa jadi\Npenyihir terkuat di keluarga kita.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.31,0:04:50.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kerja bagus selama ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.58,0:04:54.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sekarang tak ada lagi\Nyang memperlakukanmu seperti budak.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.21,0:05:01.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Andai saja kau tidak ada...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:01.75,0:05:02.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lucas!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.65,0:05:06.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau tak apa-apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.41,0:05:11.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, ternyata kau. Kukira Kakak.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.38,0:05:15.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayah.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:15.95,0:05:17.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selamat ulang tahun.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:18.01,0:05:22.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Semuanya, Jasmine akan duduk di sebelahku.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.78,0:05:26.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bakat Jasmine harus diprioritaskan.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:27.81,0:05:30.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau adalah penyihir api.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.58,0:05:33.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau pantas menjadi penerus\NKeluarga Flamesworth.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.15,0:05:36.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jasmine.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.61,0:05:37.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jasmine!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:38.45,0:05:39.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau tak apa-apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:40.01,0:05:41.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau habis melihat ilusi, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:42.71,0:05:46.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf, aku cuma sedikit kaget.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:47.15,0:05:48.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa kau melihat ilusi juga, Note?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.95,0:05:51.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak melihat apa-apa.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:52.35,0:05:54.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku cuma melihat kalian.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:55.61,0:05:57.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku ingin melindungi semuanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:58.15,0:06:00.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cuma itu keinginanku.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.43,0:06:06.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dasar Mana Beast rendahan!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.01,0:06:10.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku ini petualang Kelas AA, tahu!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.01,0:06:12.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Brald, sadarlah!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.25,0:06:16.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akhirnya ketemu.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:19.05,0:06:20.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Samantha!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.18,0:06:22.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:22.71,0:06:24.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di mana batu sihirku?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:24.71,0:06:26.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu tak ada di sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.49,0:06:27.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.05,0:06:32.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mau pulang.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.81,0:06:33.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mengerti.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.21,0:06:38.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi untuk sekarang, lindungi semuanya\Ndari kabut ini dengan sihirmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:39.38,0:06:40.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.05,0:07:03.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa kau punya sihir\Nuntuk menghapus kabut ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.91,0:07:05.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak bisa menghapusnya, tapi...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.95,0:07:08.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kurasa bisa kalau cuma untuk membuka jalan.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.18,0:07:11.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Samantha, hentikan sihirmu!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.61,0:07:21.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa yang terjadi?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:23.38,0:07:25.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa dari tadi kita tak menyadarinya?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.81,0:07:28.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ia menunjukkan ilusi dengan kabutnya
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.05,0:07:30.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,untuk menggiring kita sampai ke sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.85,0:07:35.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Augmenter Kelas AA sepertiku
Dialogue: 10,0:07:35.51,0:07:38.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,takkan kalah dari tanaman besar!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.41,0:07:44.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Brald, jangan menyerang sembarangan!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.25,0:07:48.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kesadarannya masih terpengaruh efek kabut.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.75,0:07:51.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Samantha, kau bantu Lucas!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:53.11,0:07:54.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lucas!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.35,0:07:56.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mengerti.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:08.81,0:08:11.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sihirku tak mempan?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.85,0:08:14.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Elijah, Reginald!\NTolong urus bagian belakang!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.81,0:08:17.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku dan Jasmine akan membuka jalan.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.41,0:08:18.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.89,0:08:39.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dengan ini mungkin bisa.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:39.87,0:08:40.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jasmine!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:48.01,0:08:49.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa dia...?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.71,0:08:52.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita akan terobos dan keluar dari sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.35,0:08:54.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan melindungi semuanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:55.11,0:08:57.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak mau kehilangan siapa pun.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.65,0:08:59.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:59.85,0:09:00.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Brald!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.15,0:09:09.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.61,0:09:11.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah tak bisa lagi?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.15,0:09:13.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lucas!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.35,0:09:14.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mengerti.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.45,0:09:22.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Daya sebar apinya memang luas,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:23.55,0:09:27.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi tak bisa menguapkan air di dalamnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:28.15,0:09:30.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kemungkinan akarnya ada di dalam tanah
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.95,0:09:34.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan mengandung banyak sekali air.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.81,0:09:39.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Samantha, bisa kau kumpulkan air\Ndi dalam akarnya dengan sihirmu?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.65,0:09:40.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akan kucoba.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:49.58,0:09:51.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Regenerasinya terhenti?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.05,0:09:55.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.75,0:10:01.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita cari Criol, lalu keluar dari sini\Nsecepat mungkin.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:01.58,0:10:04.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, dia pasti masih hidup.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:04.75,0:10:06.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah, sialan!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.45,0:10:09.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa tak ada yang berjalan sesuai rencana?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:09.65,0:10:12.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Katanya kalian petualang veteran?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.01,0:10:14.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku takkan ikut kalau tahu bakal begini!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:15.21,0:10:18.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku jadi begini karena ditipu oleh kalian!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:18.81,0:10:19.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lucas!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:21.85,0:10:23.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Clara itu siapa?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:23.45,0:10:25.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mantan tunangan Criol.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.41,0:10:27.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mantan?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:27.45,0:10:29.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia tewas di dalam dungeon.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.85,0:10:33.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Criol datang ke sini untuk mewujudkan\Nmimpi mendiang tunangannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:34.21,0:10:36.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku juga ingin mewujudkan mimpinya.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:37.71,0:10:39.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Makanya, Brald juga?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:44.58,0:10:45.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kabutnya...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.55,0:10:46.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mustahil.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:48.81,0:10:50.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa pun yang kita lakukan tetap percuma.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.18,0:10:54.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Uapkan air di akarnya dengan api yang kuat
Dialogue: 10,0:10:54.14,0:10:56.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,untuk melemahkan pergerakannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:56.61,0:10:58.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita masih bisa menyelamatkan Criol.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:09.01,0:11:10.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:12.35,0:11:13.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mungkinkah...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:14.75,0:11:15.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu tak mungkin benar, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:16.15,0:11:19.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa Mana Beast Kelas S ada di sini?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.51,0:11:22.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku cuma pernah melihatnya di buku.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:25.78,0:11:27.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dewa Pelindung, Elder Wood.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:33.98,0:11:36.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, kabutnya berasal dari Beast itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.95,0:11:42.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Criol?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.18,0:11:45.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Clara, jangan pergi.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:47.15,0:11:48.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Criol.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.81,0:11:51.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu pasti cuma ilusi, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.45,0:11:52.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:52.65,0:11:54.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini adalah kenyataan.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.91,0:11:58.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Beast sekelas kau...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:58.25,0:12:00.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sama sekali tak takut!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:09.95,0:12:11.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Brald!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:15.05,0:12:17.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hentikan! Kita tak bisa melawannya!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:20.98,0:12:22.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Note!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.38,0:12:29.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa-apaan ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.45,0:12:32.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak pernah diberi tahu\Nakan jadi seperti ini!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.91,0:12:39.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Elijah!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.38,0:12:48.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo kita keluar dari sini berdua saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.01,0:12:49.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jasmine?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.38,0:12:50.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana dengan mereka?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.25,0:12:52.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau pasti paham, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.98,0:12:54.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mustahil menyelamatkan semuanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:56.95,0:12:58.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sudah berjanji
Dialogue: 10,0:12:59.21,0:13:01.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,untuk kembali bersama-sama.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:01.51,0:13:02.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.05,0:13:05.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,sudah berjanji kepada keluargamu!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.05,0:13:10.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sudah berjanji.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.81,0:13:16.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku berjanji akan melindungimu kali ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:26.25,0:13:27.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pohon besar sialan!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:31.71,0:13:33.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita akan keluar dari sini
Dialogue: 10,0:13:34.01,0:13:36.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,bukan hanya berdua,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.61,0:13:38.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi bersama semua orang.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:53.61,0:13:56.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Elijah, tolong bantu Brald!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:56.31,0:13:58.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita akan kabur bersama dari pintu masuk!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.81,0:13:59.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mengerti!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:17.75,0:14:18.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa
Dialogue: 10,0:14:19.41,0:14:21.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,ia mengincar mereka berdua?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.71,0:14:29.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Criol!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.91,0:14:37.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Takkan ada habisnya kalau kita\Ntak menyerang tubuh aslinya.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.45,0:14:40.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi air yang mengalir di tubuhnya
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.58,0:14:43.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,tak bisa ditembus dengan sihir.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.45,0:14:45.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:46.98,0:14:50.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,akan kubakar dengan sihir\Nyang lebih kuat dari api.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.81,0:15:20.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo kita keluar selagi bisa.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.35,0:15:25.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Note, itu...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:29.25,0:15:30.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Note!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:35.18,0:15:37.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku bahkan tak bisa membakarnya\Nsampai habis, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:38.15,0:15:39.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Seharusnya tak seperti ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:43.85,0:15:44.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Reginald!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:47.01,0:15:49.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lucas, bakar akarnya!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.45,0:15:52.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Seharusnya tak seperti ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.38,0:15:53.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cepat, Lucas!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.81,0:16:00.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lucas, kau tak apa-apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.31,0:16:12.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini bukan diriku yang sesungguhnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:13.18,0:16:15.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lucas, tolong Samantha!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:20.91,0:16:23.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku adalah keturunan bangsawan murni.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:28.31,0:16:29.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mata itu...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.45,0:16:33.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku kenal orang dengan mata seperti itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.01,0:16:39.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yang harus kulakukan
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.38,0:16:42.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,adalah bertahan hidup\Ndan jadi penyihir terhebat.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:42.45,0:16:45.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu adalah tugas mereka yang lahir\Ndi Keluarga Wykes.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:47.78,0:16:50.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau ingin melindungi semuanya, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:51.05,0:16:51.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:51.98,0:16:55.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,jadilah umpan agar aku bisa selamat.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:55.98,0:16:57.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Matanya...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.71,0:17:07.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, dia memilih jalan itu, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:12.09,0:17:13.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Note!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.89,0:17:14.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jasmine!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.65,0:17:18.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa yang kau lakukan?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:23.45,0:17:25.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Untuk kalian para rakyat jelata,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:25.85,0:17:28.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,apa kalian kira aku mau\Nmempertaruhkan nyawaku?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:29.21,0:17:32.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nyawaku lebih berharga daripada kalian.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:32.85,0:17:34.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukankah kita ini teman?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.91,0:17:37.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Teman?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.21,0:17:41.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian itu cuma bawahan yang harusnya senang
Dialogue: 10,0:17:41.55,0:17:43.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,karena bisa jadi umpan untukku.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:43.61,0:17:45.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini akan tercatat dalam sejarah.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:46.94,0:17:47.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lucas.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.31,0:17:56.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Seberapa beraninya kalian...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:56.15,0:17:58.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan sampaikan itu pada semuanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.05,0:18:04.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak mau mati.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:04.71,0:18:06.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak mau mati!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.75,0:18:11.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hadapi aku!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.71,0:18:33.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Brald?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:38.65,0:18:39.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Note.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:51.05,0:18:53.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya sudah tak ada pilihan lain.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:19.51,0:19:23.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bahkan Tetua Virion dari Elenoir saja
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.55,0:19:26.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,butuh puluhan tahun\Nuntuk menguasai kekuatan ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:47.65,0:19:48.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayah.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:49.45,0:19:53.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Entah aku bisa bertahan hidup atau tidak\Njika memakai kekuatan ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.58,0:20:01.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi aku sudah berjanji\Nakan melindungi semuanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:30.55,0:20:32.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Absolute...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:32.75,0:20:33.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Zero!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:48.99,0:20:50.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:53.78,0:20:56.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Elder Wood yang membuat ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:31.91,0:22:34.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mustahil ini...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:34.31,0:22:35.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:35.91,0:22:37.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Arthur...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:41.98,0:22:43.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Note.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:44.51,0:22:47.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak mungkin dia hanya Augmenter Kelas A.
